    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[They say ‘nobody likes change’… but maybe you’re the opposite. You’re looking for a fresh start, a new industry or a different role at work. Or maybe change was forced on you – and you’ve had to deal with being made redundant. Or perhaps you’ve been waiting for that promotion, but the right opportunity just hasn’t happened yet. ]]></Value>
